snippet.title: Nintendo 64DD Review - Japan Pro Golf Tour 64 - H4G
snippet.description:
Hard4Games reviews the FINAL N64DD Game: Japan Pro Golf Tour 64, one of the rarest N64 DD titles.  Certainly one of the most expensive!

-------

We produce the in-depth reviews on the old-school games you love.
H4G Game Reviews is a YouTube channel featuring high quality and unique gaming videos! We cover rare and retro games, game collecting, as well as modern gaming topics & reviews! Come game with us!
